name: Eyetraction II
description:
īˈtrakSH(ə)n (eyetraction) “Eye-traction” is a word combination of eye and attraction. It is a visualization of a quality or force of someone or something that tends to pull others in or create interest in the person or thing. Specifically in the visual art. This is a collaboration work of Alphabad and Stefany Zefanya. 

Digital & Watercolor 4000 x 4000 px 

Personal use only.
